parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.It’s a good thing you were here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Helping people is what I do, Sister.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.You and I are a lot alike. I too have dedicated my life to helping those in need.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I guess you’re right. But we go about it in different ways.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I like problem solving… I’m pretty good at it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.I bet you are. You’ve shown it tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.But sometimes… our best isn’t good enough.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.I spoke with Madalyn… In Cape Vedra.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.After the storm, Father Parker and Madalyn went missing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.I tracked down Madalyn and went to visit her… But something was different.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.I sensed she was hiding… She didn’t want to be found.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.It was later I heard from the police.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.Madalyn murdered the priest at Cape Vedra.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.I know. She had a hidden life. She used me… And I didn’t see it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Madalyn used you to groom kidnap victims?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.Yes. I thought I was helping them… But…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.It’s okay, Judy. It wasn’t your fault. You are a kind person.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.I feel so guilty. I was doing the work of the devil and I didn’t even know it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.But now there’s a chance to find her, and stop her from hurting anyone else.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.In hindsight, I see that Madalyn was manipulative.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.Our convent was split, and we looked at each other with suspicious eyes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The other nuns… You didn’t trust them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.I did my best to keep the peace. But so many became paranoid of outsiders.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.We were told to never discuss our lives with the students.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Do you think Madalyn could be demon possessed?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaOp.I’m surprised to hear you ask that. I didn’t think you believed in such things.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Let’s just say, I’ve become more open-minded.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.I did not think of her as possessed… but she seemed cold, almost like life was missing from her eyes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’ve heard from people close to her that she has been possessed by a demon… Someone who also possessed her brother.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaOp.Brother? Madalyn did not have a brother, as far as I knew.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.From what I’ve heard, the priest was her brother.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I don’t think Madalyn and the priest were who you thought they were.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.You mentioned before that you had visions. Do you remember what they were?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.I was visited by an angel in my dreams.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.It was something more. It felt real…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.I was in a courtyard, surrounded by clouds, and she appeared to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.She said she was going to guide me and that the world was in danger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.She had glowing white wings and long flowing blonde hair.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McShEx.The glowing thing we found in the attic… Ever since I found it, she’s appeared to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.Perhaps this angel is tied to what we found.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She is… She called it the Oracle of the Seraph.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuShEx.She’s a high order being… She’s a being of purity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.In the teachings we learned that the angels closest to God were the Seraphs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.They are pure, and can see through the eyes of God.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Without sin. As perfect as the Lord himself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.1Hero! Perhaps now is not a good time to utter curses.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.You’ve been chosen. She will guide you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.You are becoming closer to God. I see it in you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.For the sake of those she’s hurt, please stop her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Sounds like I have good on my side.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It’s getting late. Perhaps I should leave you alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Do you have other plans this evening?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrDe.Oh. I might be out a little longer before I go home.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.You are a hard worker. I’m glad you’re helping bring peace to Madalyn’s victims.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.Please do. I very much like your company.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Of course I did. I was looking forward to spending some time with my favorite nun.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.You know, 1Hero, what you did in the forest was really brave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.First I save you from spiders and now I'm saving you from demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.Oh, 1Hero. Mother Superior... She is an evil woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaDe.What she did to me in the woods... It has brought evil thoughts into my mind.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoDe.I don't know how to describe it... a desire... for sin.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It's okay, Judy. You're safe now. Father can protect you from demons.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.You know, 1Hero, perhaps you should remove your jacket. Unless you plan to leave so soon?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Oh, right. I might as well make myself comfortable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.You know, perhaps you can help me again with the plant.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.We need to get you a step stool.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Of course. I am so forgetful of my needs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrCl.Oh, uhh... Thank you for the kind words.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp.Sorry, Sister Judy, I’ve not seen it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I enjoyed our time together, 1Hero, but I need some time to think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I enjoyed our time together, 1Hero, but I need some time to think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.Thank you for being there for me, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.Thank you for being there for me, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.We found a basement… But it’s dark. You better stay up here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.1Hero… I should really get back to my studies.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrCl.I must confess, I told Chloe about our little bedroom fun.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.I’m sure Chloe will have a story for you too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.How could I end the night without visiting my favorite Sister?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.What were you ladies discussing while I was gone?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx.I was just talking about how crazy Hannah was.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You better keep her away from sports if you value your safety.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.That’s not what she told me about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.Come on, Judy. Let’s not freak him out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.I would love to visit this cave you found, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.What!? I tell her lots of stuff… She’s my councilor.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.Oh, Chloe. You can not keep secrets from the boy.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.Judy… You’re not lying to Chloe, are you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.What did you do? You have to tell me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.It’s nothing… 1Hero just helped me, that’s all.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.I think you both have some issues that you need to resolve.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.1Hero… He showed me how to… touch myself.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I didn’t mean to! It was just… I needed to know.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.It’s unhealthy to keep these feelings bottled up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChSaCl.I don’t know… I don’t know how to feel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Sounds like maybe you need a lesson too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Since I’m here… It wouldn’t hurt to show you both some new tricks.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoCl.Judy! Maybe you shouldn’t be so into this.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.You can trust him, Chloe. He was a great help to me.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.You’re a good woman, Sister Judy. You care for people, and that counts for something.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I’ve enjoyed your company, but I think I need a moment to myself. There is much to process.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I understand. I’m here for you whenever you need someone to talk to. ");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Chloe, do you want me to walk you home?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I hope she’s not using all the hot water.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeShOpNo1.1Hero!? I thought the nun was in here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Are you done with the shower? What’s taking so long?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Can you ladies keep an eye on her?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.We need to regulate her body temperature?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Don’t overthink it. Just make sure she doesn’t hurt herself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp^.We’ll have her better in no time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaBaDe^.Can’t say I understand; but if I can keep Hannah alive, I can keep this girl alive.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx^.I will stay by her side as well.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoEx.It’ll take a while to clean up this mess.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.But it’s so late. Where are you going to sleep, Sister Judy?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChHaEx.Yeah! I’d love to show you my place.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Thank you so much, Chloe. You are a life-saver.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx.I’m sure my mom would love to meet you too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Don’t worry, Judy. We’ll help you clean up your room once things dry up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFlEx.Maybe 1Hero would like to come over to my place too.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Yeah. It’ll be fun. We’ll keep your mind off of this leak.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We did. Father Zephaniah had a secret safe…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We just need to figure out how to open it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.I hope you find what you’re looking for.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No, not bleach… We can clean it with something else that won't damage the carpet or sheets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.It smells so bad. I hope we can clean it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaEx.You know, we have a bed here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.She’s sick. But we’ll fix her up real soon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChSaCl.Poor Judy. I hope we can help her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChSaEx.I want to go see the basement, but I know Judy would follow me.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.I feel an urge to go see this basement… But I know it’s too dangerous.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.The basement connects to the cave system.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.Yeah. But it’s more complicated than that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl^.Are we safe? Could the building collapse?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.The cave’s been here for thousands of years. I doubt anything is collapsing.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnOp.What the hell is my wife doing down there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I need to ask a big favor from all of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Don’t go down there, and let’s keep all of this a secret.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.But, just in case, I’m going to get some officers over here to keep guard.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.There is a basement under my bedroom?");
